<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/10/urban-armor-gear-uag-iphone-12-max-pro-mini-civilian-series-cases">Urban Armor Gear 发布 iPhone 12 手机壳，获军用等级防撞认证</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1372261" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hy.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hy.jpg 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hy-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/hy-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
